These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, ritmeester, cain, bongani
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, november, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, yellow, turquise, ebony
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, doctor, nurse, writer
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
 2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes ebony is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
 7. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
 8. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 9. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
10. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the journalist and the game-smoker##7
11. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the writer##5
13. the writer is the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | bongani    | ritmeester | cain    | game   |
| Birthday   | july | november | january | december |
| Color           | yellow       | turquise   | ebony  | purple     |
| Job     | journalist      | nurse   | writer    | doctor    |

