 8. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
10. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the fan reggae##5
11. the police-officer is the fan blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
