 9. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
11. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
12. the person who growspoppy is the person drinking lemonade##1

