 5. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
 6. the fan folk is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 7. the person traveling to paris is somewhere between the fan rock and the fan folk##7
 8. the person traveling to miami is not the fan rock##6
 9. the fan dubstep is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the fan folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| City         | colone      | paris   | miami   | rome       |
| Beverage   | mirinda | fanta    | soy-milk | lemonade       |
| Color   | white  | blood-red | azure   | ebony     |
| Music-Genre         | rock   | techno    | folk   | dubstep |

