.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, blue, orange, lilac
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, documentary, disaster, comedy
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, montecristo, alhambra, blend
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, mirinda, soy-milk
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who likes orange##1
 3. the person drinking cola is the blend-smoker##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes blue##2
 5. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5
 6. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person who likes mauve##7
 7. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
 8. the fonseca-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
10. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color   | lilac      | orange     | blue   | mauve    |
| Movie-Genre     | comedy | disaster   | documentary | epic |
| Cigar     | blend        | alhambra     | fonseca  | montecristo      |
| Beverage   | cola       | soy-milk | lemonade   | mirinda    |

 